query:
SELECT 
  id,
  dataVenda,
  TYPEOF(dataVenda) as tipo,
  FROM_UNIXTIME(dataVenda/1000) as data_convertida,
  valorTotal,
  excluido
FROM vendas
WHERE excluido = 0
ORDER BY dataVenda DESC
LIMIT 10
